            "title": "UK retail sales drop more than expected in May",
            "description": "<html><body><p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li><p id=\"description\">Retail sales in the UK dropped 2.70% in May over the previous month, a bigger fall compared to consensus estimates of a 0.5% decline.</p></li>\n<li><p id=\"description\">Year-over-year, the figure declined 1.3%.</p></li>\n<li>ETFs: (NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FXB\">FXB</a>), (NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EWU\">EWU</a>), (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FKU\">FKU</a>), (BATS:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EWUS\">EWUS</a>), (NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FLGB\">FLGB</a>)</li>\n<li>Currency: (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GBP:USD\" title=\"British Pound / US Dollar\">GBP:USD</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
